e worlds second largest processor and marketer of chicken beef and pork after jbs sa and annually exports the largest percentage of beef out of the united states together with its subsidiaries it operates major food brands including jimmy dean hillshire farm sara lee ball park wright brand aidells and state fair contents  profile  acquisitions  tyson renewable energy  corporate charity  religious activities  corporate governance  board of directors  ceos  controversies  environmental record  employment of undocumented immigrants  price manipulation  undisclosed use of antibiotics  employee abuse  animal abuse  see also  references  external links profileedit the company was established by john w tyson in  and benefitted during world war ii when chicken was not included in foods that were rationed as of  the company employs  people who work at more than  facilities  of which are in the us as of  tyson had about  employees in  states locations are concentrated in the midwest with  locations in arkansas  in texas  in iowa and the remainder of the mostly eastern us with less than  locations tyson also works with  independent contract chicken growerscitation needed it is one of the largest us marketers of valueadded chicken beef and pork to retail grocers broad line foodservice distributors and national fast food and full service restaurant chains fresh beef and pork frozen and fully cooked chicken beef and pork products caseready beef and pork supermarket deli chicken products meat toppings for the pizza industry and retail frozen pizza club store chicken beef and pork ground beef and flour tortillas it supplies yum brands chains that use chicken including kfc and taco bell as well as mcdonalds burger king wendys walmart kroger iga beef obradys small restaurant businesses and prisonscitation needed the company makes a wide variety of animalbased and prepared products at its  food processing plants it produces many different products including buffalo wings boneless buff