et leader in the retail and food service markets it serves providing products and service to customers throughout the united states and more than  countries tyson has approximately  team members employed at more than  facilities and offices in the united states and around the world john h tyson was born on september   in springdale arkansas he is the son on don and jean tyson and the grandson of john w tyson the founder of tyson foods inc after graduating from springdale high school in  john attended the university of arkansas where in  he was initiated into the arkansas alpha chapter john later transferred to smu where he received a bachelor’s degree in business administration john has worked in the family business since his early teens and became a member of the board in  today he is chairman of the board of tyson foods and has served in that capacity since  under john’s direction tyson foods has emerged as the world’s largest proteinprocessing company largely on the strength of the  acquisition of ibp a giant processor of beef and pork that acquisition engineered by john accomplished a long time family goal – namely to successfully diversify the company beyond the confines of the poultry business by early  tyson foods was producing roughly  of all the meat products consumed in the united states brother tyson has been honored with the woodrow wilson award for corporate citizenship he has been named man of the year by the arkansas poultry industry by the arkansas easter seals and by the art center of the ozarks he was also named humanitarian of the year by the national conference for community and justice john serves on numerous boards and committees including walden woods project the advisory board for the yale center for faith and culure university of arkansas and as committee chairman of the university of arkansas capital campaign for the st century for his long and continued support of the free enterprise system phi delta theta honored john h tyson with the nancemillett “free enterprise” award at the  general convention learn about other famous phis calendar aug  tue allday assumption of mary assumption of mary aug  allday   sep  mon allday labor day labor day sep  allday   oct  wed allday feast of st francis of assisi feast of st francis of assisi oct  allday   copyright   phi delta theta fraternity  kansas state university designed by rockettheme john h tyson born september   executive  prabook create biography you can add biographies of your relatives friends people you admire as well as your own biography log in once logged in you can add biography in the database directories newly added edit profile general education career works life stance personality connections references people also searched for karen parfitt hughes helen hunt betsy vogel boze trammell crow nastia liukin regina taylor john h tyson executive john h tyson american food products executive named man of year arkansas poultry industry  board directors area united way supporter farm aid volunteer activities for wellbeing and education of arkansas children member of arkansas poultry federation past president american meat institute national association manufacturers background tyson john h was born on september   in springdale arkansas united states son of don and jean tyson education bachelor of business administration southern methodist university  career complex manager north carolina area tyson foods inc springdale arkansas vice president marketing corporation accounts purchasing manager retail sales manager northeast states president beef and pork division president chairman tyson foods inc  president chairman chief executive officer — chairman chief executive officer — chairman since  political liaison to washington and little rock tyson foods inc membership board directors area united way supporter farm aid volunteer activities for wellbeing and education of arkansas children member of arkansas poultry federation past president american meat inst